In order to help us write these pages questionnaires were sent out to the 48 houses in our 12 sq.km area. We received 32 of these back at school.
The most popular hobby by far was {gardening,}but as might be expected in such a beautiful area other outdoor pursuits were well represented, including{fishing, shooting, walking, {horse riding, beekeeping, sailing, {photography and studying wildlife. }
Indoor pastimes included{sewing, {reading, wine making and woodwork.} There are several{folk musicians} living locally who sing and play such diverse instruments as accordian, fiddle, mandoline, appalachian dulcimer, penny whistle and several guitars. There is a very popular folk evening each Thursday at Oxen Park.
